name: Careless and Well-Intentioned by Tyler Hobbs

metadata.name: Careless and Well-Intentioned #0
metadata.description:
Careless and Well-Intentioned is a series of four unique iterations, plus an artist's proof, produced from a single generative algorithm.

This iteration is the artist's proof.

Artist: Tyler Hobbs  
Year: 2022  
Medium: Algorithmic Design  
Dimensions: 15000 x 18000 px
